Scripts included from other projects:

pre-tokenizer.perl : from Moses
tokenizer.perl : from europarl tools.tgz
normalize-punctuation.perl : from wmt12 tools


fetch.sh will grab the corpora from the internet and extract the necessary files
to various subdirectories under ./corpora.

./run.sh can then be run immediately.

Alternately, you can download/extract them yourself and set the variables in run.sh
appropriately.

